&lt;p&gt;London&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expect total first-year compensation ranging from £48,500-£57,500 (average to high performance) consisting of (i) annual base salary of £41,500 and (ii) uncapped variable compensation linked to individual performance.&lt;/li&gt;
